# Keeps `triton/model_repository/` present in git so the bind-mount in
# docker-compose.yaml works on a fresh clone before the build script runs.
# The build script (`scripts/build-trt-engine.sh`) populates this directory
# with the inflight_batcher_llm template + the compiled `.engine` file.
# That generated content is gitignored — see ../../.gitignore.
